WEBVTT

01:55.800 --> 01:56.720
No need to fight.

01:58.120 --> 01:59.800
Because we got tricked too.

02:43.200 --> 02:44.280
No problem.

02:45.120 --> 02:46.120
One more.

02:57.400 --> 02:59.320
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

03:04.480 --> 03:07.800
What that disciple
at Weimiao Pavilion said was false.

03:07.880 --> 03:09.440
She was deceived by Xiaowei too.

03:11.440 --> 03:14.040
You found the talisman
in Li Mao's hand, didn't you?

03:16.040 --> 03:16.920
That's right.

03:18.440 --> 03:20.560
If it were really as that disciple said,

03:21.080 --> 03:23.760
and his wife, who asked
for the talisman, had torn it up,

03:23.840 --> 03:26.760
how could the talisman
have ended up in Li Mao's hand?

03:30.440 --> 03:32.720
Before Wangyan and I
came to the Wei mansion,

03:32.800 --> 03:34.760
we'd already investigated
the three victims.

03:35.560 --> 03:37.040
When they died,

03:37.560 --> 03:39.240
they were all clutching a love talisman.

03:40.840 --> 03:41.680
So the truth is

03:41.760 --> 03:44.240
that the one under the spell
will suffer the blowback

03:44.320 --> 03:45.440
only if they tear
the talisman up themselves?

03:45.520 --> 03:48.760
Wei Qing's death proves that too.

03:50.040 --> 03:51.160
Which means

03:51.240 --> 03:53.760
Li Mao died because he tore up
the talisman himself.

03:59.240 --> 04:01.840
How could you use
something this filthy on me?

04:02.720 --> 04:03.840
How could you?

04:07.200 --> 04:08.840
<i>Once someone is targeted</i>
<i>by a love talisman,</i>

04:08.920 --> 04:12.600
<i>their heart will be slowly eroded</i>
<i>by the Fox-Allure Spell within it.</i>

04:13.400 --> 04:15.320
And once the talisman is destroyed,

04:15.400 --> 04:19.200
the person under the spell
will die from unbearable heartache.

04:19.279 --> 04:21.079
Only Xiaowei knew the truth,

04:22.880 --> 04:25.200
so she must've been the one
who switched the talismans.

04:25.880 --> 04:27.400
She wanted Wei Qing dead.

04:28.840 --> 04:30.640
With everyone who wanted to catch
Xiaowei gathering in the Wei mansion,

04:31.240 --> 04:32.760
the protective barrier you set up,

04:32.840 --> 04:34.680
and the Ice Curse in play,

04:34.760 --> 04:36.960
she didn't dare use
demon magic recklessly.

04:38.240 --> 04:40.200
But she still wanted Wei Qing dead,

04:40.280 --> 04:43.240
so she had to leverage the blowback
of the Fox-Allure Spell.

04:44.080 --> 04:47.640
The Ice Curse's true name
is the Never-Ending Curse.

04:47.720 --> 04:49.560
Anyone who betrays the Formless Moon Sect

04:49.640 --> 04:52.640
will be hunted
by this curse for all eternity.

04:52.720 --> 04:54.120
The Never-Ending Curse?

04:56.280 --> 04:58.880
Didn't you read widely
back at the Shilin Sect?

04:59.600 --> 05:00.440
Haven't you read about it?

05:01.840 --> 05:03.600
I can be a bit playful sometimes.

05:04.960 --> 05:05.800
"Sometimes"?

05:08.160 --> 05:09.200
Shut up.

05:13.040 --> 05:14.360
The Never-Ending Curse

05:16.360 --> 05:19.680
is the Formless Moon's
cruelest form of punishment.

05:21.080 --> 05:23.640
People often compare moonlight
to things such as water,

05:24.160 --> 05:25.480
frost,

05:26.360 --> 05:27.480
and mist.

05:28.640 --> 05:31.520
And the members of the Formless Moon
take surnames like Wu,

05:32.040 --> 05:34.040
Lu, Xue,

05:34.560 --> 05:35.560
Shuang,

05:36.200 --> 05:37.200
and Bing

05:38.360 --> 05:40.880
as they move through the mortal world.

05:41.400 --> 05:43.240
Once we violate the sect's laws,

05:43.320 --> 05:46.760
the moonlight transforms into our surname

05:48.680 --> 05:50.800
and hunts us for eternity.

05:52.480 --> 05:54.720
The Never-Ending Curse can reach

05:55.400 --> 05:57.440
wherever the moonlight can,

05:58.120 --> 05:59.840
and it won't stop until we're dead.

06:00.760 --> 06:02.880
Xiaowei's surname is Bing,

06:03.560 --> 06:07.280
so what pursues her is the Ice Curse.

06:07.920 --> 06:09.400
Once it catches up to her,

06:09.480 --> 06:11.280
she'll be turned into ice

06:11.360 --> 06:13.160
and shattered into pieces.

06:15.680 --> 06:16.520
What's your surname?

06:19.520 --> 06:21.880
Lu, as in dew.

06:23.840 --> 06:25.120
My name

06:26.080 --> 06:27.440
is Lu Wuyi.

06:29.120 --> 06:30.120
That's a beautiful name.

06:32.200 --> 06:33.200
I'll remember it.

06:39.800 --> 06:41.920
As long as Xiaowei
doesn't use demon magic,

06:42.000 --> 06:44.000
the Ice Curse won't lock onto her.

06:44.080 --> 06:46.160
But there is one exception.

06:50.200 --> 06:51.600
Around the full moon,

06:52.120 --> 06:54.640
the moonlight is strongest,
and so is its power.

06:55.240 --> 06:57.280
Even if Xiaowei doesn't use demon magic,

06:57.360 --> 06:59.160
the Never-Ending Curse
will still sense her.

06:59.760 --> 07:02.760
That means she'll have
to hide in dark places

07:03.360 --> 07:04.320
to avoid the moonlight.

07:06.880 --> 07:08.600
Yesterday was the 15th.

07:08.680 --> 07:10.160
Today is the 16th.

07:10.680 --> 07:11.960
That means…

07:12.040 --> 07:14.400
The moon is the fullest
on the 16th night of the month.

07:15.400 --> 07:17.120
Wangyan and I hurried back

07:18.240 --> 07:20.800
to enjoy tonight's moonlight.

07:22.080 --> 07:23.280
I imagine

07:24.560 --> 07:26.120
it'll be beautiful.

07:52.680 --> 07:54.080
You stayed behind,

07:54.600 --> 07:56.000
but you're not saying anything.

07:56.880 --> 07:57.920
What's on your mind?

07:58.560 --> 08:00.000
I'm thinking about you--

08:00.520 --> 08:01.920
You're thinking about me?

08:03.640 --> 08:05.280
I'm thinking about how you had
the audacity to come back.

08:06.440 --> 08:08.600
-And what if I hadn't come back?
-If you hadn't,

08:09.200 --> 08:10.360
I would've dragged you back myself.

08:10.440 --> 08:12.760
Then you'd better keep a close eye on me.

08:12.840 --> 08:15.360
Once I'm gone, I won't be easy to find.

08:16.800 --> 08:18.040
How about I tie you up?

08:18.680 --> 08:21.160
Want to try the Demon-Binding Rope again?

08:33.880 --> 08:35.280
What's that on your arm?

08:35.799 --> 08:37.679
A mark from the Formless Moon.

08:39.280 --> 08:40.240
Is it a moon phase?

08:42.640 --> 08:45.000
It looks like the full moon.

08:45.760 --> 08:47.880
But I prefer to call it Wangyue.

08:50.760 --> 08:51.720
Wang, as in hope?

08:53.920 --> 08:55.680
As in gazing until your eyes go dry.

09:01.320 --> 09:02.520
Do all the sect members have one?

09:02.600 --> 09:05.440
Everyone except Wuyi has one.

09:06.960 --> 09:10.680
This mark will be with us
for life after life.

09:28.000 --> 09:28.840
Here.

09:42.560 --> 09:43.960
I've heard

09:44.600 --> 09:47.640
that everyone in the Formless Moon
has a mark on their arm.

09:49.040 --> 09:50.440
Why don't you have one?

09:53.760 --> 09:55.360
Because my moon phase

09:56.080 --> 09:56.920
is Hui.

09:57.880 --> 09:58.800
Hui?

10:00.680 --> 10:02.320
I've read

10:02.400 --> 10:04.320
that the Formless Moon
has seven moon phases.

10:04.400 --> 10:07.320
Waning gibbous, full, last-quarter,

10:07.400 --> 10:11.040
waning crescent, waxing crescent,
first-quarter, and waxing gibbous.

10:11.760 --> 10:13.600
I've never heard of Hui as a moon phase.

10:17.520 --> 10:20.000
When you can't see the moon at night,

10:20.920 --> 10:22.160
that moon phase

10:23.000 --> 10:24.040
is Hui.

10:25.440 --> 10:27.120
That's why I don't have a mark.

10:28.520 --> 10:30.080
Hui, as in regret?

10:32.040 --> 10:33.640
Hui, as in obscure and hard to understand.

10:35.600 --> 10:37.880
But it doesn't matter
if I'm hard to understand.

10:38.680 --> 10:39.880
There's one person

10:41.360 --> 10:42.280
who understands me.

10:46.840 --> 10:49.280
Actually, I don't really understand you.

10:52.800 --> 10:54.240
I mean my sister, Wangyan.

10:55.920 --> 10:58.080
She knew I didn't have
a moon phase on my arm,

10:58.160 --> 11:01.160
so she said she'd give me one.

11:02.600 --> 11:04.480
This hollow jade jue

11:05.080 --> 11:06.640
is like the new moon.

11:07.920 --> 11:11.200
So Xiaowei has a moon phase too?

11:11.720 --> 11:13.360
Of course she does.

11:14.720 --> 11:16.720
Back then, to make sure
she could find her savior,

11:17.400 --> 11:20.960
she branded him
with the same mark she bore herself.

11:21.640 --> 11:23.560
That way, even through life and death,

11:23.640 --> 11:27.040
even if he vanished into the crowd
and his appearance changed,

11:27.120 --> 11:29.960
she could still find him
through that mark.

11:30.040 --> 11:34.000
Do you remember what you have to do
to ask Lady Wei for a love talisman?

11:37.000 --> 11:39.720
Take off your clothes
and bare yourself completely.

11:44.720 --> 11:47.720
So, that's to look for the mark?

11:47.800 --> 11:50.200
You catch on quick, Shiguang.

11:52.640 --> 11:53.880
Then what is Xiaowei's moon phase?

11:54.480 --> 11:55.360
Kui,

11:57.560 --> 11:59.120
as in indebted.

11:59.840 --> 12:01.000
The waning gibbous moon?

12:03.880 --> 12:05.480
I think I've seen it somewhere before.

12:42.200 --> 12:43.480
I'm looking at the flowers.

12:44.640 --> 12:45.960
What are you looking at?

12:49.560 --> 12:53.560
I've noticed several times before
that you often stare at flowers in a daze.

12:54.200 --> 12:55.520
Do you like flowers a lot?

12:56.880 --> 12:58.560
Do you like flowers a lot?

13:04.040 --> 13:06.440
They all like gold, silver,

13:06.520 --> 13:07.800
fine silk, and satin.

13:09.000 --> 13:10.040
But I

13:12.920 --> 13:14.040
only like flowers.

13:14.960 --> 13:17.480
But no matter how beautiful
a flower is, it'll still wither.

13:18.400 --> 13:19.440
It can't last forever.

13:20.680 --> 13:22.360
And that's exactly why

13:23.160 --> 13:24.440
it's more beautiful

13:25.760 --> 13:26.960
and more precious.

13:29.240 --> 13:30.080
Don't you think so?

13:32.120 --> 13:33.080
Miss Lu,

13:34.720 --> 13:35.640
have we really never met?

13:37.840 --> 13:38.960
Should we

13:40.280 --> 13:41.360
have met?

13:45.440 --> 13:47.320
Your hand is dirty.
Let me wipe it for you.

14:20.840 --> 14:23.360
Miss Lu, let me ask you one more time.

14:24.920 --> 14:28.200
Before we came here, did we ever meet?

14:30.880 --> 14:32.400
I don't remember.

14:33.000 --> 14:35.840
Miss Lu, your heart is racing.

14:36.360 --> 14:38.080
Are you lying?

14:41.120 --> 14:42.520
If I'm the one lying,

14:44.600 --> 14:46.000
why are you blushing?

14:47.040 --> 14:47.880
So…

14:48.400 --> 14:49.880
So are you admitting it?

14:51.240 --> 14:54.680
Back then,
you had this rag doll with you too.

14:55.760 --> 14:59.320
There aren't many grown men
who still play with dolls.

14:59.840 --> 15:02.600
You were too memorable to forget.

15:04.080 --> 15:06.040
It's no ordinary doll.

15:08.160 --> 15:12.080
It's been my loyal companion
since childhood.

15:13.240 --> 15:14.360
So you do remember me.

15:16.480 --> 15:18.040
But my memories of you

15:18.840 --> 15:20.280
have been blurry.

15:23.760 --> 15:24.960
Why is that?

15:29.640 --> 15:32.280
Here's a bouquet of wildflowers in bloom.

15:32.360 --> 15:33.560
Cheer up.

15:38.800 --> 15:39.880
Forget me.

15:47.480 --> 15:48.800
Maybe…

15:50.320 --> 15:52.560
you've just met too many pretty girls.

15:54.440 --> 15:56.120
Are you calling yourself pretty?

15:57.880 --> 15:59.760
You are pretty. Very pretty.

15:59.840 --> 16:01.200
You don't have to say it. I'll say it.

16:03.720 --> 16:04.560
Instead of doing your job,

16:05.320 --> 16:07.520
you're here admiring flowers
and playing with the doll?

16:08.240 --> 16:09.520
You scared me!

16:10.360 --> 16:13.280
When did you get here?
How much did you hear?

16:15.320 --> 16:17.320
Isn't the real business
supposed to wait until tonight?

16:19.360 --> 16:20.240
By the way,

16:21.240 --> 16:23.600
there is something
I really need your help with, Ji.

16:24.680 --> 16:25.520
Tell me.

16:27.160 --> 16:30.160
This is the note Xiaowei used to lure me
to the workshop and frame me.

16:31.440 --> 16:32.280
COME TO THE WEAVING
WORKSHOP THIS AFTERNOON

16:32.360 --> 16:33.160
THE DEADLOCK CAN BE BROKEN - XIAOWEI

16:34.800 --> 16:35.960
That's outrageous.

16:38.320 --> 16:40.760
Investigate the handwriting on this note
and see if it gives us any clues.

16:47.920 --> 16:48.840
You really know how
to order people around.

16:48.920 --> 16:49.880
Just go already.

16:56.000 --> 16:57.280
That's just how he is.

17:13.520 --> 17:16.599
If the moon doesn't come out all night,

17:17.200 --> 17:20.400
won't our plan fail?

17:29.240 --> 17:31.480
What… What are you doing?

17:32.120 --> 17:34.280
Master Wei's body should be placed
in the ancestral hall,

17:34.360 --> 17:36.680
then buried and laid to rest
after the funeral.

17:36.760 --> 17:38.280
What exactly are you trying to do here?

17:39.160 --> 17:40.360
Everyone, stay calm.

17:40.440 --> 17:43.360
Master Wei was killed by a demon.

17:43.440 --> 17:46.680
His spirit can only rest
after the evil influence is purged.

17:46.760 --> 17:48.280
Before dawn,

17:49.080 --> 17:51.040
everyone must remain in the courtyard

17:51.760 --> 17:54.600
and help purify and guide
Master Wei's soul.

18:00.400 --> 18:01.400
Purifying the soul.

18:30.960 --> 18:31.960
Guiding it onward.

18:51.480 --> 18:53.320
All of you were close to Master Wei.

18:53.960 --> 18:56.240
You must remain
in the courtyard until dawn.

18:56.960 --> 18:57.840
Then the ritual will be complete.

18:59.840 --> 19:00.960
Don't worry.

19:02.200 --> 19:04.200
I'll stay by your side here.

19:05.080 --> 19:06.160
You won't be in danger.

19:16.040 --> 19:18.000
They should've started by now, right?

19:18.520 --> 19:20.280
A night hunt for Xiaowei…

19:20.800 --> 19:21.960
Wangyan, that's really brilliant.

19:23.680 --> 19:26.600
But can they really handle it?

19:28.040 --> 19:29.240
Shouldn't we go take a look?

19:29.960 --> 19:31.960
Are you worried about them

19:32.040 --> 19:35.640
or just bored staying here?

19:37.960 --> 19:39.480
You saw right through me again.

19:40.520 --> 19:41.920
Not fun at all.

19:44.760 --> 19:47.400
We've already exposed our identities.

19:47.480 --> 19:49.800
We can't let Xiaowei find out
we've come back.

19:50.800 --> 19:51.840
Just stay put.

19:52.520 --> 19:55.280
Don't forget that we're waiting here

19:55.800 --> 19:57.720
because there's something else
we need to do.

19:59.040 --> 20:01.680
All right, I'll do as you say, Wangyan.

20:09.680 --> 20:11.760
-I need to relieve myself.
-Can't you wait?

20:11.840 --> 20:12.840
I'll go with you.

20:12.920 --> 20:14.520
Xiaowei still hasn't been caught.

20:15.120 --> 20:16.120
If you go alone,

20:16.200 --> 20:17.520
it could be dangerous.

20:17.600 --> 20:19.520
I'm the descendant
of a military commander.

20:19.600 --> 20:20.920
Why would I fear some seductive fox demon?

20:21.600 --> 20:22.800
You stay here and mind things.

20:23.400 --> 20:26.040
A grown man following me
to the latrine? Ridiculous.

20:27.040 --> 20:28.600
He should go with you.

20:29.360 --> 20:30.320
Otherwise,

20:31.160 --> 20:32.600
we would be worried.

20:47.600 --> 20:48.920
Ms. Yu, where are you going?

20:51.160 --> 20:52.200
The wind is strong tonight.

20:52.720 --> 20:53.840
I'm going back to my room to get a cloak.

20:56.080 --> 20:56.920
All right.

21:05.920 --> 21:06.960
On a starless, moonless night like this,

21:07.640 --> 21:09.400
what are you looking at, Steward Luo?

21:10.880 --> 21:12.280
With no stars and no moon,

21:13.560 --> 21:15.120
and night at its darkest,

21:16.000 --> 21:17.360
I'm just a little afraid.

21:40.920 --> 21:42.600
Mr. Liu, you've been looking up nonstop.

21:43.960 --> 21:46.160
What exactly are you looking at?

21:47.400 --> 21:48.840
I wanted to admire the moon.

21:50.560 --> 21:51.920
Too bad

21:52.000 --> 21:54.040
these tactless clouds

21:54.800 --> 21:57.800
have hidden away
all that beautiful moonlight.

21:59.640 --> 22:01.760
So you enjoy moon-watching, Mr. Liu?

22:02.720 --> 22:06.000
Then how come you stay in your room

22:06.560 --> 22:08.240
and never go out most nights?

22:10.000 --> 22:11.200
I go to bed early.

22:14.840 --> 22:16.440
The moonlight is dim tonight,

22:17.240 --> 22:18.600
and it's hard to see clearly.

22:19.320 --> 22:21.360
I'd better lead the way for you,

22:21.880 --> 22:23.440
so we can head back sooner.

22:53.880 --> 22:55.960
I just slipped and fell.

22:56.600 --> 22:58.880
If you won't help me up, fine.

22:58.960 --> 23:01.440
But why do you look
like you want to eat me alive?

23:12.080 --> 23:14.200
Ever since Wei Qing passed,

23:15.000 --> 23:17.120
the Wei household has fallen apart.

23:17.920 --> 23:20.120
The servants have all grown lazy.

23:21.120 --> 23:23.040
They won't even clean up
the standing water in the corridor now.

23:59.200 --> 24:00.320
The ritual isn't over yet.

24:01.080 --> 24:02.280
Where are you going, Steward Luo?

24:03.160 --> 24:04.400
To the dye workshop.

24:05.000 --> 24:06.440
In the middle of the night?

24:06.520 --> 24:08.440
You may not know this, Master Wu,

24:08.520 --> 24:10.640
but dye-making is a complicated process.

24:10.720 --> 24:14.000
How long the materials need to soak
depends on the weather and temperature.

24:14.080 --> 24:15.000
They have to be checked constantly.

24:16.160 --> 24:18.880
Master Wei may be gone,

24:18.960 --> 24:23.040
but the Wei family's business
still has to go on, doesn't it?

24:24.520 --> 24:25.840
In a household this large,

24:26.480 --> 24:29.000
do you really need to handle
such minor matters yourself?

24:30.760 --> 24:32.920
Too many tragedies
have struck the household lately.

24:33.880 --> 24:36.080
The servants are already demoralized.

24:36.160 --> 24:37.120
Business comes first.

24:37.880 --> 24:39.040
Let Steward Luo go.

24:47.640 --> 24:48.800
I'll go with you.

24:52.360 --> 24:53.480
Steward Luo.

25:00.440 --> 25:01.640
Thank you for your hard work.

25:01.720 --> 25:03.840
It's cold at night. Keep yourself warm.

25:08.240 --> 25:09.360
Thank you.

25:23.800 --> 25:24.640
Where's Ms. Yu?

25:25.680 --> 25:27.400
She went back to her room to get a cloak.

25:30.160 --> 25:31.160
I'll go check on her.

25:46.560 --> 25:49.280
<i>The servants have all grown lazy.</i>

25:49.880 --> 25:52.160
<i>They won't even clean up</i>
<i>the standing water in the corridor now.</i>

25:54.840 --> 25:55.760
Just as I thought.

25:57.120 --> 25:58.920
Fox demons really do love to lie.

26:03.920 --> 26:04.840
Not good.

26:05.760 --> 26:06.880
Only Ji Ling is with him.

26:10.320 --> 26:11.680
You gave her your outer robe.

26:12.200 --> 26:13.280
Aren't you cold?

26:15.240 --> 26:17.200
When the heart is warm,
the body doesn't feel cold.

26:18.640 --> 26:19.760
Do you really have one?

26:21.960 --> 26:22.920
Have what?

26:23.960 --> 26:24.840
A heart.

26:28.240 --> 26:29.760
If you really like her,

26:30.280 --> 26:33.240
you can't just do little things
like bringing her tea and water.

26:33.760 --> 26:35.200
That won't move her.

26:37.000 --> 26:38.960
If you have something to say, just say it.

26:39.040 --> 26:41.360
I'm a warrior. I like things direct.

26:41.440 --> 26:45.240
I can't stand people
beating around the bush.

26:46.040 --> 26:47.240
It gives me a headache.

26:48.680 --> 26:50.760
If you like her that much,

26:50.840 --> 26:54.240
why not just go to Weimiao Pavilion
and ask for a talisman?

26:58.920 --> 27:00.880
Can love won through a talisman

27:01.920 --> 27:03.160
really be called love?

27:03.240 --> 27:05.560
It'll be nothing but an illusion.

27:05.640 --> 27:08.040
You're a clever man, Master Ji Ling.

27:08.120 --> 27:09.840
Surely you can see that too.

27:10.800 --> 27:13.960
Since you know that love
forced by a talisman is false,

27:15.040 --> 27:16.280
why do you think

27:16.800 --> 27:18.600
the head of Weimiao Pavilion

27:19.760 --> 27:22.280
goes to such lengths to do all this?

27:23.840 --> 27:26.080
Then you'd have to ask her.

27:29.440 --> 27:30.760
I am asking.

27:37.560 --> 27:38.880
Why are you so nervous?

27:39.640 --> 27:42.360
Are you the head of Weimiao Pavilion?

27:48.360 --> 27:49.720
Are you Xiaowei?

27:53.160 --> 27:55.800
MOONLIT RADIANCE

27:59.680 --> 28:03.200
They all say Steward Luo
is indispensable to the Wei household.

28:03.720 --> 28:05.640
You handle everything yourself,

28:05.720 --> 28:06.680
even the account books,

28:07.360 --> 28:09.320
recording every detail personally.

28:10.400 --> 28:11.720
I'm the steward.

28:11.800 --> 28:13.640
It's only right
that I keep the books myself.

28:13.720 --> 28:15.360
What are you implying, Master Li?

28:19.320 --> 28:20.840
I have a note here.

28:25.600 --> 28:27.160
The handwriting on it

28:27.240 --> 28:30.280
matches the writing
in your account books exactly.

28:30.880 --> 28:32.120
I'd like you to take a look.

28:48.200 --> 28:49.640
I've never seen this note before.

28:50.280 --> 28:51.760
I went to the fabric house

28:51.840 --> 28:53.600
and compared it with your ledger.

28:54.520 --> 28:56.080
It is your handwriting.

28:56.800 --> 28:58.320
What you may not know, Master Li,

28:59.120 --> 29:01.720
is that while I know a bit
about weaving and tailoring,

29:01.800 --> 29:03.040
I've never had any schooling.

29:03.760 --> 29:06.840
Master Wei was kind enough
to teach me to read and write.

29:07.360 --> 29:09.920
He even gave me copybooks in his own hand
for me to practice from.

29:10.760 --> 29:12.040
So strictly speaking,

29:13.160 --> 29:14.920
the handwriting on this note

29:15.520 --> 29:17.280
looks more like Master Wei's.

29:19.360 --> 29:20.440
The servants said

29:20.960 --> 29:22.920
you were the last person

29:24.400 --> 29:26.800
to enter his room before Master Wei died.

29:28.920 --> 29:30.040
That's not true.

29:31.080 --> 29:32.240
They were mistaken.

29:36.280 --> 29:37.400
The fox demon…

29:38.440 --> 29:39.600
It's the fox demon!

29:57.320 --> 29:58.600
Why isn't she out yet?

30:03.040 --> 30:05.680
GOLDEN WEAVE

30:35.800 --> 30:36.640
Wuyi!

30:48.880 --> 30:50.000
Master Wu,

30:51.160 --> 30:52.320
what are you doing?

30:52.920 --> 30:54.320
And what are you doing?

30:56.040 --> 30:58.560
I've been kneeling so long,
my legs went numb.

30:59.160 --> 31:00.720
I just wanted to get up and stretch.

31:01.440 --> 31:02.400
Still acting?

31:03.560 --> 31:04.400
Admit it. You are…

31:04.480 --> 31:06.600
Ms. Yu has been attacked by the fox demon.

31:21.760 --> 31:22.880
Are you really not…?

31:27.120 --> 31:27.960
Did we get it wrong?

31:28.520 --> 31:30.600
The demon… The fox demon…

31:30.680 --> 31:31.880
The fox demon is in the dye workshop!

31:33.440 --> 31:35.120
Li Jie is fighting it!

31:38.000 --> 31:39.000
Li Jie…

32:05.040 --> 32:07.640
-Li Jie, is there really a fox demon?
-There was,

32:07.720 --> 32:09.240
but then it suddenly disappeared.

32:09.840 --> 32:10.920
How is that possible?

32:29.000 --> 32:29.920
Wangyan,

32:30.600 --> 32:32.000
the moon is out.

33:24.640 --> 33:25.560
Break!

33:37.760 --> 33:39.760
If you don't want
the Ice Curse to consume you,

33:39.840 --> 33:41.120
stop using demon magic.

33:42.120 --> 33:43.360
Show your true form,

33:44.320 --> 33:45.720
Liu Weixue.

33:58.240 --> 33:59.560
So it really is Liu Weixue.

34:00.680 --> 34:02.880
But I was with him
the whole time just now.

34:02.960 --> 34:04.800
Did he use Word Magic on me?

34:07.440 --> 34:08.960
He wouldn't dare.

34:09.600 --> 34:12.520
Otherwise,
the Ice Curse would've come long ago.

34:13.320 --> 34:16.360
Then why did he suddenly use demon magic
and reveal his demon form?

34:16.880 --> 34:17.840
Xiaowei,

34:19.400 --> 34:21.040
it's been a while.

34:25.120 --> 34:26.080
How…

34:27.280 --> 34:29.120
How did you figure me out?

34:29.199 --> 34:31.480
We went down the wrong path at first

34:31.560 --> 34:33.800
and thought Xiaowei was a woman.

34:34.400 --> 34:37.400
Otherwise,
we would've caught you long ago.

34:38.000 --> 34:41.480
Xiaowei,
you'd hidden yourself well all along.

34:42.000 --> 34:43.719
But on the wedding night,

34:43.800 --> 34:45.120
you couldn't resist using demon magic,

34:45.199 --> 34:47.840
and that drew the Ice Curse.

35:12.360 --> 35:13.160
Vile demon!

35:25.320 --> 35:26.360
<i>That night,</i>

35:26.880 --> 35:28.480
<i>all of us saw</i>

35:28.560 --> 35:31.000
<i>Xiaowei being chased by the Ice Curse,</i>

35:31.080 --> 35:32.520
<i>and its back foot got frostbitten.</i>

35:35.600 --> 35:37.360
-It hurts. It hurts.
-<i>You were clever.</i>

35:37.440 --> 35:40.120
Feigning drunkenness,
you pretended to twist your ankle

35:40.200 --> 35:42.800
to cover up the injury
caused by the Ice Curse.

35:43.480 --> 35:45.640
An ordinary sprain heals in a few days.

35:46.480 --> 35:49.320
But frostbite from that curse
is much harder to recover from.

35:49.920 --> 35:51.560
Just now, when I went
with you to the latrine,

35:51.640 --> 35:53.760
I noticed you were
still having trouble walking.

35:55.680 --> 35:57.560
You saw I was getting suspicious,

35:58.200 --> 36:00.160
so you lied and said there
was standing water on the ground

36:00.240 --> 36:01.720
and that you'd slipped.

36:01.800 --> 36:04.520
That's not the only way
you gave yourself away.

36:04.600 --> 36:06.520
Demons can wear countless human guises,

36:06.600 --> 36:09.120
but their demonic nature
is hard to change.

36:09.960 --> 36:12.240
Habits and preferences
formed over hundreds of years

36:12.320 --> 36:15.320
certainly can't be changed overnight.

36:15.400 --> 36:17.440
Young Master Liu has lived
in comfort since childhood.

36:17.520 --> 36:19.680
He only sleeps on tussah silk bedding.

36:20.200 --> 36:24.200
A martial artist
can sleep rough and eat rough.

36:24.280 --> 36:27.360
No way someone like that
would sleep only on tussah silk.

36:28.000 --> 36:29.600
Lady Wei really lives in luxury.

36:29.680 --> 36:32.200
All her bedding is made of tussah silk.

36:35.200 --> 36:36.720
So comfortable.

36:38.440 --> 36:39.760
Xiaowei severed
the spiritual tail long ago

36:39.840 --> 36:41.880
and lost the sense of smell.

36:41.960 --> 36:43.520
You can smell that from that far away?

36:57.840 --> 36:59.520
What about now?

37:00.960 --> 37:02.480
Go wash up.

37:05.800 --> 37:06.920
I see.

37:07.880 --> 37:09.600
I'll go bathe right now.

37:09.680 --> 37:11.160
<i>What Ms. Yu smelled</i>

37:11.240 --> 37:13.000
<i>was actually the scent of the weasel demon</i>

37:13.080 --> 37:14.760
<i>inside Wu Shiguang's Cosmic Pouch.</i>

37:14.840 --> 37:16.200
<i>After Li Jie took the pouch away,</i>

37:16.280 --> 37:18.920
<i>Wu Shiguang no longer smelled of it.</i>

37:19.000 --> 37:21.720
But you still pretended you could smell it
and kept lying

37:21.800 --> 37:24.400
to hide the fact
that you'd lost your sense of smell.

37:24.920 --> 37:25.960
Xiaowei,

37:26.800 --> 37:28.800
are you still going to deny it?

37:43.280 --> 37:44.360
Shengwei?

37:45.040 --> 37:46.080
How did this happen?

37:47.160 --> 37:48.040
Shengwei.

37:48.120 --> 37:50.400
Shengwei! Shengwei…

37:51.320 --> 37:53.480
You clearly killed her
by ripping out her heart.

37:54.080 --> 37:54.920
Drop the act.

37:55.600 --> 37:57.720
That's not true. That's not true.

37:58.480 --> 37:59.720
Shengwei.

37:59.800 --> 38:02.000
Shengwei. Wake up, Shengwei!

38:02.080 --> 38:04.080
Shengwei! Shengwei…

38:04.160 --> 38:06.680
I didn't do it. Untie me! Shengwei!

38:07.600 --> 38:08.600
Untie me!

38:38.720 --> 38:40.120
She's still alive.

38:41.000 --> 38:44.480
But her heart is badly damaged,
and she's lost too much blood.

38:44.560 --> 38:47.400
My seal will only slow
the bleeding for a short while.

38:47.480 --> 38:49.040
It can't save her.

38:49.640 --> 38:52.080
It can only buy her a little more time.

38:52.600 --> 38:54.240
I saw the wound
on the left side of her chest

38:54.320 --> 38:56.480
and thought she'd stopped breathing,
so I didn't stay.

38:56.560 --> 38:59.760
How is she still alive now?

39:01.640 --> 39:02.840
You did it.

39:03.840 --> 39:05.280
You killed her.

39:06.600 --> 39:08.680
Fox demon, I'll kill you!

39:22.520 --> 39:24.200
I wanted to repay her.

39:25.680 --> 39:27.800
How could I ever hurt her?

39:31.600 --> 39:34.720
She's the Wang Sheng
I've searched for across lifetimes.

40:18.040 --> 40:20.360
A packed bundle.

40:24.280 --> 40:25.120
Chestnut cakes.

40:27.560 --> 40:29.160
A shadow puppet.

41:08.480 --> 41:10.640
So, as it turned out,

41:11.360 --> 41:13.080
Ms. Yu was Wang Sheng.

41:13.800 --> 41:19.040
But then why is there a waning moon mark
on Wei Qing's sole?

41:20.040 --> 41:21.480
That's only an old scar.

41:34.720 --> 41:36.640
<i>Scars can be erased with magic.</i>

41:37.520 --> 41:39.000
But a Formless Moon mark

41:40.000 --> 41:41.320
can never be removed.

41:41.400 --> 41:42.880
It remains lifetime after lifetime.

41:45.960 --> 41:47.000
You discovered it

41:47.080 --> 41:48.920
when you attacked Ms. Yu
half a month ago, didn't you?

41:59.920 --> 42:00.760
But

42:01.840 --> 42:03.120
it was already too late.

42:14.280 --> 42:16.360
<i>I had already granted</i>
<i>a love talisman to Wei Qing.</i>

42:17.320 --> 42:18.560
<i>I never imagined</i>

42:19.200 --> 42:20.640
<i>that by doing so,</i>
<i>I'd be signing a death warrant</i>

42:20.720 --> 42:22.120
<i>for the one I'd been searching for.</i>

42:28.200 --> 42:30.040
<i>I couldn't let Shengwei die,</i>

42:30.680 --> 42:33.680
<i>so I came to the Wei mansion.</i>

42:34.520 --> 42:35.600
<i>I needed to make sure she'd</i>

42:35.680 --> 42:37.480
<i>never suffer the blowback</i>
<i>of the Fox-Allure Spell.</i>

42:38.120 --> 42:39.200
<i>Unfortunately,</i>

42:39.280 --> 42:42.360
that's impossible.

42:42.440 --> 42:44.480
As long as the love remains,

42:45.240 --> 42:46.440
the spell can't be lifted.

42:47.280 --> 42:49.760
Even killing someone won't end it.

42:50.280 --> 42:51.360
No, it can be lifted

42:52.480 --> 42:54.200
once the one who asked for the talisman

42:55.280 --> 42:56.320
falls for someone else.

42:57.240 --> 42:58.520
I see.

42:59.680 --> 43:00.960
You used another love talisman

43:01.560 --> 43:03.840
to make Wei Qing fall for someone else.

43:04.360 --> 43:08.120
And the perfect choice happened to be
right in front of you,

43:09.400 --> 43:10.240
Luo Wei.

43:13.160 --> 43:15.640
YU SHENGWEI IS MY CLOSEST
AND DEAREST FRIEND. BY LUO WEI

43:15.720 --> 43:19.360
<i>Yu Shengwei</i>
<i>is my closest and dearest friend.</i>

43:19.440 --> 43:23.160
You knew that she and Ms. Yu
were intimate friends.

43:23.240 --> 43:25.640
Without Ms. Yu,
she could never have worked here.

43:28.200 --> 43:29.720
Luo Wei tried to break
the two of them apart

43:29.800 --> 43:31.640
not because of Master Wei,

43:32.400 --> 43:33.320
but because of Ms. Yu.

43:35.000 --> 43:36.800
<i>Everyone says</i>
<i>Weimiao Pavilion is the best place</i>

43:36.880 --> 43:37.960
<i>to pray for love.</i>

43:38.040 --> 43:40.160
If I went to ask for a talisman,

43:40.760 --> 43:41.960
would your heart…

43:44.000 --> 43:46.200
Would your heart finally be mine?

43:50.720 --> 43:53.280
<i>You secretly nudged Luo Wei</i>
<i>into seeking a love talisman.</i>

43:54.320 --> 43:57.400
And so Master Wei fell for Luo Wei.

43:57.920 --> 43:58.760
After that,

43:58.840 --> 44:02.040
his feelings for Yu Shengwei
naturally disappeared.

44:02.120 --> 44:04.480
<i>Thus, the Fox-Allure Spell</i>
<i>on her was lifted.</i>

44:10.400 --> 44:13.160
But why did you still want Wei Qing dead

44:13.240 --> 44:14.520
after the spell had been lifted?

44:15.720 --> 44:18.280
Because he refused to divorce Shengwei.

44:18.360 --> 44:19.840
He wouldn't set her free.

44:20.600 --> 44:21.640
He deserved to die.

44:23.240 --> 44:25.680
You actually used the blowback
of the Fox-Allure Spell to kill.

44:26.360 --> 44:28.280
So it was you who switched the talismans.

44:29.280 --> 44:30.240
It wasn't me.

44:31.720 --> 44:32.960
It was Luo Wei.

44:33.560 --> 44:36.560
She stole
the love talisman before I could.

44:46.920 --> 44:50.280
Mr. Liu, are you looking for something?

44:50.360 --> 44:51.680
Why are your clothes in such a mess?

44:52.240 --> 44:53.160
Where's your belt?

44:54.480 --> 44:57.120
Steward Luo said
Master Wei's belt was damaged,

44:57.200 --> 44:59.120
<i>so she took it away to mend it for him.</i>

45:08.520 --> 45:09.400
It's no use.

45:12.840 --> 45:15.200
-But those demon hunters said…
-I lied to them.

45:16.160 --> 45:19.440
Only the person
under the spell can tear up the talisman.

45:20.360 --> 45:22.880
No one else can destroy it.

45:23.480 --> 45:25.440
Only if Wei Qing tears it up himself

45:26.520 --> 45:27.840
will the blowback be triggered.

45:29.040 --> 45:30.640
If you really want him dead,

45:32.080 --> 45:33.640
do as I say.

45:35.320 --> 45:36.840
You have Shengwei's sachet

45:37.680 --> 45:39.120
with you too, right?

45:41.120 --> 45:43.480
If Yu Shengwei really divorces you,

45:44.040 --> 45:46.400
you will become the laughingstock
of the entire Luo'an City.

45:46.480 --> 45:48.080
Then what should I do?

45:49.440 --> 45:50.880
How did you get her sachet?

45:52.360 --> 45:53.600
<i>I had Luo Wei</i>

45:53.680 --> 45:55.840
<i>cover the talisman</i>
<i>bearing her name and Wei Qing's</i>

45:56.360 --> 45:59.000
<i>with a thin sheet of paper</i>

46:00.400 --> 46:02.480
<i>bearing the names Wei Qing</i>

46:02.560 --> 46:04.600
<i>and Yu Shengwei.</i>

46:04.680 --> 46:07.200
Tear it up, and everything will be solved.

46:11.560 --> 46:12.880
You lied to me…

46:19.840 --> 46:20.680
<i>Your plan worked.</i>

46:21.320 --> 46:22.480
Wei Qing

46:22.560 --> 46:24.640
killed himself.

46:26.080 --> 46:30.480
Then who was the fox demon
who attacked Ms. Yu?

46:30.560 --> 46:31.800
She wasn't attacked by a fox demon.

46:31.880 --> 46:34.160
I set up a protective barrier
around the Wei mansion.

46:34.240 --> 46:36.000
If any demon had tried to cause trouble,

46:36.080 --> 46:37.760
I would've sensed it at once.

46:37.840 --> 46:40.560
A demon couldn't make a move,
but a human could.

46:45.960 --> 46:48.400
Luo Wei, you're worse than a demon.

46:49.760 --> 46:52.160
One, two, three, four.

46:52.240 --> 46:57.400
These four items hold all the secrets
behind tonight's murder case.
